```{=html}
<div id="listing-buttons" style="display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
<% for (const item of items) { %>
  <a href="<%- item.link %>" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 8px 16px; background-color: <%- item.color %>; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid <%- item.color %>;"><%- item.button %></a>
<% } %>
</div>
```
